<div class="title">Fork in the Road</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=MiKey2234&Exact=1">MiKey2234</a></div>


